OL,6,FA drug dealer who told police he was
OL,7,Finspired by the film Home Alone after
OL,8,Frigging his house with booby traps has
OL,9,Fbeen jailed.
OL,11,FIan Claughton installed trip wires and
OL,12,Fhomemade pipe bombs at his property in
OL,13,Fthe village of Grimethorpe, Barnsley,
OL,14,Fto target would-be intruders.
OL,16,FOne device was attached to a trip wire
OL,17,Fdesigned to activate an air horn.
