OL,6,FWhen police raided his property they
OL,7,Falso found an array of imitation
OL,8,Ffirearms, a crossbow and a home-made
OL,9,Fflamethrower, made from a fire
OL,10,Fextinguisher filled with petrol.
OL,12,FHand-written notes issued threats to
OL,13,Ftrespassers, including one which said:
OL,14,F"Now would be a good time to get
OL,15,Fmeasured up for your coffin and say
OL,16,Fgoodbye to loved ones."
