OL,4,C'Home Alone'-style booby traps jailed
OL,6,FIt prompted a three-day operation,
OL,7,Fwhich saw dozens of nearby properties
OL,8,Fevacuated as a 100-metre cordon was
OL,9,Fput in place while Army bomb squad
OL,10,Fexperts were called in.
OL,12,FClaughton, 59, was convicted of ten
OL,13,Foffences including possession of
OL,14,Ffirearms and explosives, drug
OL,15,Fproduction and possessing criminal
OL,16,Fproperty, at Sheffield Crown Court
OL,17,Flast November. He was jailed for seven
OL,18,Fyears.
