OL,6,FHis ex-wife Lesley Claughton, 58, was
OL,7,Falso found guilty of drug offences, as
OL,8,Fwell as possessing criminal property
OL,9,Fand purchasing an imitation firearm.
OL,10,FShe was given a 21-month suspended
OL,11,Fsentence.
OL,13,FDet Supt Al Burns, of the Yorkshire
OL,14,Fand Humber Regional Organised Crime
OL,15,FUnit, said: "Ian Claughton is someone
OL,16,Fwho was clearly involved in drugs
OL,17,Foffending to a very significant degree.
