OL,3,CDrug dealer who rigged house with
OL,4,C'Home Alone'-style booby traps jailed
OL,6,F"He appears to have developed a siege
OL,7,Fmentality that saw him go to unusual
OL,8,Fand elaborate lengths to defend his
OL,9,Fhome and its illicit contents from
OL,10,Fwould-be intruders, drawing
OL,11,Finspiration from Macaulay Culkin's
OL,12,Fcharacter in the popular Christmas
OL,13,Ffilm Home Alone."
OL,15,FThe investigation started after UK
OL,16,FBorder Force intercepted a package at
OL,17,FHeathrow Airport which had been sent
OL,18,Ffrom China addressed to Lesley
OL,19,FClaughton's home, nextdoor to her ex-
OL,20,Fhusband's in Brierley Road.
