OL,6,FThe package contained five folding
OL,7,Frevolvers - later confirmed to be
OL,8,Frealistic imitation firearms, which
OL,9,Fare illegal to import into the UK
OL,10,Fother than in certain circumstances.
OL,12,FWhen officers arrested Claughton they
OL,13,Ffound two mantraps, two potential
OL,14,Ffirearms and four large plastic bags
OL,15,Fof cannabis buds, with an estimated
OL,16,Fvalue of #16,000.
OL,18,FA cannabis farm was found hidden in a
OL,19,Fsecret room at one next-door property
OL,20,Fand 1.5kg of amphetamine was found at
OL,21,FLeslie Claughton's home.
