OL,6,FClaughton was seen demonstrating the
OL,7,Fflame thrower on a video on his phone.
OL,8,FA large amount of cash was recovered,
OL,9,Fincluding #27,000 found stitched into
OL,10,Fa sofa.
OL,12,FClaughton told officers explosive
OL,13,Fdevices were "crow scarers", similar
OL,14,Fto banger fireworks, which he had
OL,15,Fadapted by placing them in plastic
OL,16,Fpiping sealed with expanding foam and
OL,17,Fwrapped in plastic sheeting.
