OL,6,FOpening the trial to jurors last
OL,7,FOctober, prosecutor Helen Chapman
OL,8,Fsaid: "If you are sitting there
OL,9,Fthinking that this sounds a little
OL,10,Flike the film Home Alone, then you
OL,11,Fwould be correct.
OL,13,F"In fact that is precisely what Ian
OL,14,FClaughton said he was aiming for when
OL,15,Fhe told the police about these
OL,16,Fdevices."
OL,18,FClaughton's home had previously been
OL,19,Ftargeted by burglars, who were
OL,20,Fbelieved to be looking for cannabis.
