OL,6,FHe told officers he had ordered the
OL,7,Fimported "switch guns" believing they
OL,8,Fwere blank firers that he intended to
OL,9,Fuse at a themed birthday party.
OL,11,FHe said the amphetamine was his to use
OL,12,Ffor weight loss and chronic fatigue,
OL,13,Fand that he had been growing the
OL,14,Fcannabis under duress.
OL,16,FHelen Wragg, senior Crown prosecutor
OL,17,FYorkshire and Humberside, said: "Ian
OL,18,Fand Lesley Claughton ran a significant
OL,19,Fdrugs operation from their properties,
OL,20,Fgoing to extraordinary lengths to
OL,21,Fprotect their illegal enterprise.
