OL,6,F"The traps, explosives, and weapons
OL,7,Ffound were not props from a film, but
OL,8,Freal devices capable of causing
OL,9,Fserious harm.
OL,11,F"We worked closely with the police to
OL,12,Fbuild a case which proved that Ian
OL,13,FClaughton's arsenal of weapons was
OL,14,Fspecifically designed to protect his
OL,15,Fdrug empire from would-be intruders.
