OL,6,FDet Supt Emma Wheatcroft, of South
OL,7,FYorkshire Police, said: "This incident
OL,8,Fcaused some real concern and
OL,9,Fdisruption within the community of
OL,10,FGrimethorpe, with some residents
OL,11,Fhaving to be evacuated from their
OL,12,Fhomes.
OL,14,F"I would like to again express our
OL,15,Fthanks to those residents and the
OL,16,Fwider local community for their
OL,17,Fsupport while our officers worked
OL,18,Falongside colleagues from the YHROCU
OL,19,Fand other emergency services to make
OL,20,Fthe area safe again."
